gene_sets <- list()
gene_sets[["glucolysis_regulated"]] <- glucolysis_regulated
gene_sets[["glucose_metabolism"]] <- glucose_metabolism
gene_sets[["mitochondrial"]] <- mitochondrial
gene_sets[["oxidative_stress"]] <- oxidative_stress
gene_sets[["sanin_antigen_processing"]] <- sanin_antigen_processing
gene_sets[["phagocytosis"]] <- phagocytosis
gene_sets[["sanin_phagosome"]] <- sanin_phagosome
gene_sets[["sanin_oxidative_stress"]] <- sanin_oxidative_stress
gene_sets[["oxidative_phosphorylation"]] <- oxidative_phosphorylation
gene_sets[["lymphocyte_activation"]] <- lymphocyte_activation 
gene_sets[["myeloid_activation"]] <- myeloid_activation 
gene_sets[["oxidative_stress_redox"]] <- oxidative_stress_redox
score_mat <- vector()
for (name in names(gene_sets)){

  orig_genes <- gene_sets[[name]]
  common_genes <- orig_genes[orig_genes %in% colnames(scaled_mat)]
  pat_mat <- scaled_mat[, common_genes]

  pat_score <- rowSums(pat_mat)
  score_mat <- cbind(score_mat,pat_score)
}
plot_score_mat <- t(score_mat)
colnames(plot_score_mat) <- colnames(srt)
rownames(plot_score_mat) <- names(gene_sets)
plot_score_mat[, 1:5]

for (name in names(gene_sets)){
  srt[[name]] <- plot_score_mat[name,]
  p <- VlnPlot(srt, features = name, group.by = "RNA_snn_res.0.4", 
          cols = colors, pt.size = 0,
        ) + ylab("") + xlab("") +
    theme(text = element_text(size = 20), 
          legend.position = "none", 
          axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 0, vjust = 0.5, hjust=0.5, size = 20, color = "black"),
          axis.text.y = element_text(size = 20, color = "black")) +
   ggtitle(gsub("_"," ", str_to_title(name)))
  print(p)
}
